#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/static/src/components/open_expense_issuing_terms.xml:0
msgid ""
"You agree to indemnify and hold Odoo, its directors and officers, and "
"affiliates harmless\n"
"                    from any losses, claims, or liabilities related to your "
"use of Stripe Issuing services, including misuse or violations."
msgstr ""
"Hyväksyt korvaavasi Odoolle, sen johtajille ja virkailijoille sekä "
"tytäryhtiöille kaikki\n"
"                    Stripe Issuing -palveluiden käyttöön liittyvät "
"menetykset, vaatimukset tai velat, mukaan lukien väärinkäyttö tai "
"rikkomukset."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/static/src/components/open_expense_issuing_terms.xml:0
msgid ""
"You are fully liable for any negative balance on your Stripe Issuing "
"account.\n"
"                    Repayment is due immediately upon notice."
msgstr ""
"Olet täysin vastuussa Stripe Issuing -tilisi negatiivisesta saldosta.\n"
"                    Maksu on suoritettava välittömästi ilmoituksen saatuasi."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/static/src/components/open_card_receive_terms.xml:0
msgid ""
"You are responsible for all transactions made with your card,\n"
"                    including unauthorized charges unless covered by law or "
"Stripe’s policy."
msgstr ""
"Olet vastuussa kaikista kortillasi tehdyistä tapahtumista,\n"
"                    myös luvattomista veloituksista, ellei laki tai Stripen "
"käytäntö toisin määrää."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "You can't change the card type once the card has been created."
msgstr "Kortin tyyppiä ei voi muuttaa kortin luomisen jälkeen."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "You can't change the delivery address once the card has been shipped."
msgstr "Toimitusosoitetta ei voi muuttaa kortin lähettämisen jälkeen."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid ""
"You can't change the employee of an active card. Please create a new card "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"Aktiivisen kortin työntekijää ei voi muuttaa. Luo sen sijaan uusi kortti."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid ""
"You can't delete a card that already exists for Stripe, please block it "
"instead"
msgstr "Et voi poistaa korttia, joka on jo olemassa Stripessa. Voit estää sen"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense_stripe_card.py:0
msgid "You can't set the card state back to draft."
msgstr "Et voi palauttaa kortin tilaa luonnokseksi."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/account_payment_method_line.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot delete a payment method line that is used by an active/paused "
"card."
msgstr ""
"Et voi poistaa maksutapariviä, jota aktiivinen/tauotettu kortti käyttää."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot delete an expense that was created from a Stripe card transaction."
msgstr "Stripe-korttitapahtumasta luotua kulua ei voi poistaa."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot duplicate an expense that was created from a Stripe card "
"transaction."
msgstr "Stripe-korttitapahtumasta luotua kulua ei voi monistaa."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid "You cannot edit the security fields of an expense manually"
msgstr "Et voi muokata kulun turvakenttiä manuaalisesti"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#: model:ir.model.constraint,message:hr_expense_stripe.constraint_res_company_constraint_journal_stripe_activated
msgid ""
"You cannot remove the journal used by Stripe Issuing when it is activated"
msgstr ""
"Et voi poistaa Stripe Issuing -käyttämää päiväkirjaa, kun se on aktivoitu"

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/product_product.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot set a cost on a product that is used as an Expense card category. "
"Please duplicate it instead."
msgstr ""
"Et voi määrittää hintaa tuotteelle, jota käytetään kulukorttiluokkana. "
"Monista se sen sijaan."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot split an expense that is reserved. Please wait for the "
"transaction to be captured."
msgstr "Et voi jakaa varattua kulua. Odota, kunnes tapahtuma on tallennettu."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/models/hr_expense.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot submit an expense that is reserved. Please wait for the "
"transaction to be captured."
msgstr "Et voi lähettää varattua kulua. Odota, kunnes tapahtuma on tallennetu."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/__init__.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot uninstall the 'Expense cards' module while there are active or "
"inactive Stripe cards. Please manually block all cards before uninstalling "
"the module."
msgstr ""
"Et voi poistaa 'Kulukortit'-moduulia, jos Stripe-kortteja on olemassa "
"aktiivisena tai passiivisena. Estä kaikki kortit manuaalisesti ennen "
"moduulin poistamista."

#. module: hr_expense_stripe
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/hr_expense_stripe/static/src/components/open_card_receive_terms.xml:0
